bib_record.title: Asymmetry in angular distributions of photoneutrons from medium-weigth and heavy nuclei.

free_txt: - Eng.trans.of YF,20,242,1974
Angular and energy distributions of photoneutrons
from Rh-103, Ta-181, Au-197, Bi-209 are measured at
bremsstrahlung gamma-irradiation with end-point energy
E=28.5 MeV. The measured energy spectra are compared
with the energy spectra of neutrons produced in
identical conditions at the end-point energy E=20 MeV.
